            "b": 542.3299999999999,
            "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"
          },
          "charspan": [
            0,
            327
          ]
        }
      ],
      "orig": "Hydra is a family of Layer-2 protocols designed to scale Cardano-style eUTXO ledgers by allowing a small set of participants to run an isolated, high-throughput state channel called a Hydra Head. Transactions inside a Head settle instantly among participants and are only reconciled with the main chain when the Head is closed.",
      "text": "Hydra is a family of Layer-2 protocols designed to scale Cardano-style eUTXO ledgers by allowing a small set of participants to run an isolated, high-throughput state channel called a Hydra Head. Transactions inside a Head settle instantly among participants and are only reconciled with the main chain when the Head is closed."
    },
