            "b": 419.93,
            "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"
          },
          "charspan": [
            0,
            302
          ]
        }
      ],
      "orig": "A Hydra Head moves through four phases: Init, Open, Close, and Fanout. During Init, participants commit UTXOs from the main chain. During Open, participants exchange signed snapshots off-chain. Close posts the latest snapshot on-chain, and Fanout distributes the final UTXO set back to the main ledger.",
      "text": "A Hydra Head moves through four phases: Init, Open, Close, and Fanout. During Init, participants commit UTXOs from the main chain. During Open, participants exchange signed snapshots off-chain. Close posts the latest snapshot on-chain, and Fanout distributes the final UTXO set back to the main ledger."
    },
