          "charspan": [
            0,
            287
          ]
        }
      ],
      "orig": "Because every state transition inside the Head requires unanimous signatures from all participants, Hydra can be used as a synchronous settlement layer over Cardano-style eUTXO state: once all parties sign a snapshot, that state is final among them even before it touches the main chain.",
      "text": "Because every state transition inside the Head requires unanimous signatures from all participants, Hydra can be used as a synchronous settlement layer over Cardano-style eUTXO state: once all parties sign a snapshot, that state is final among them even before it touches the main chain."
