            296
          ]
        }
      ],
      "orig": "Hydra Heads assume an honest majority is not required; instead, safety relies on unanimity and a contestation period during Close. If a participant posts a stale snapshot, any other participant can contest it on-chain within the contestation window by presenting a newer, validly signed snapshot.",
      "text": "Hydra Heads assume an honest majority is not required; instead, safety relies on unanimity and a contestation period during Close. If a participant posts a stale snapshot, any other participant can contest it on-chain within the contestation window by presenting a newer, validly signed snapshot."
    },
